5. Layered Frontend Architecture
A. Presentation layer
Contains screens, widgets, and UI state.

B. Domain layer
Contains business entities, use cases, and rules.

C. Data layer
Contains API services, repositories, DTOs, and local cache handlers.

D. Core layer
Contains constants, theme, utilities, error handling, and base classes.

